      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Shape the <strong>pea & mint potato mixture</strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> cakes</p><p>Add the <strong>pea & mint potato cakes</strong> to a lightly oiled baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden</p><p>Tip: If the potato cake mix is a little wet and not sticking together nicely, add a spoonful or two of flour</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624294621722-x200.jpg",
