            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potato cakes are cooking, add the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper, add it to the dressing and give it a gentle mix up</p>",
      "order": 5,
