      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, crack the <strong>eggs</strong> into the pan and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Tip: Give your eggs a little shake before you crack for perfectly centred yolks!</p><p>Cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p>",
